<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.8">
<l>nārā riṇṭai nāṇma larkoṇṭu namtamarkāḷ</l>
<l>ārā vaṉpō ṭemperu māṉū raṭaimiṉkaḷ</l>
<l>tārā vārum vārpu ṉalmēyt tuvayalvāḻum</l>
<l>kūrvāy nārai pēṭai yoṭāṭuṅ kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our people, bringing day[-fresh] flowers and rope-like garlands</l>
<l>With unsating love, take refuge in the city of our great lord,</l>
<l>In Kuṟuṅkuṭi where the sharp-beaked stork plays with the hen</l>
<l>Prospering in fields, grazing in wide waters where ducks abound.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
